<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AHRAP70A4606006" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Pregled senzora brzine prednjih i stražnjih kotača na vozilu
</title>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Netočan napon i/ili pogrešan spoj uzrokuje oštećenje senzora brzine kotača.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A4606006001">
<title>
Pregled izlaznog napona
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Odspojite negativni (–) kabel s akumulatora.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Malo podignite vozilo.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Odvojite konektor senzora brzine kotača (1).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Postavite mjerne uređaje kao što je to prikazano na slici.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A460014.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "58.891mm" ver = "02" gw = "214" gh = "150"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.472in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[A]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Konektor senzora brzine kotača (pogled: [a])
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
2.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Otpor (100 &#937;)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Napajanje (12 V)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Izmjerite napon na oba kraja otpora bez okretanja kotača. Ako rezultat provjere ne odgovara propisanom, provjerite senzor, upareni enkoder i stanje ugradnje.
</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>
Napon pri otporu (100 &#937;-a) bez okretanja kotača
</title>
<ptxt>
600 do 800 mV ili 1200 do 1600 mV
</ptxt>
</spec>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Izmjerite napon na oba kraja otpora uz okretanje kotača i provjerite da su visoki (1) i niski (2) napon u skladu s propisima. Potvrdite da valni oblik nije neuredan.
</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>
Napon pri otporu (100 &#937;) s okretanjem kotača
</title>
<ptxt>
Niski napon: 600 do 800 mV
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Visoki napon: 1200 do 1600 mV
</ptxt>
</spec>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A460015.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.101mm" ver = "01" gw = "161" gh = "131"/>
</figure>
</s1>
